%% Mirror of 06-gate-first-bpmn.d2; D2 owns layout/styling, Mermaid owns reviewability.
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> G1_ClaimDictionary
  G1_ClaimDictionary --> G2_SourceCoverage: claim typed
  G2_SourceCoverage --> G3_EditionCheck: source card attached
  G3_EditionCheck --> G4_LegalL3: current edition checked
  G4_LegalL3 --> G5_CollisionReview: legal wording allowed
  G5_CollisionReview --> G6_FactualDuration: no unresolved collision
  G6_FactualDuration --> G7_ScenarioSignoff: duration basis separated
  G7_ScenarioSignoff --> G8_ExternalRefreshQA: non-additive scenario signed
  G8_ExternalRefreshQA --> ReadyForMinistryReview: snapshot regenerated

  G2_SourceCoverage --> Blocked: missing source
  G3_EditionCheck --> Blocked: edition pending
  G5_CollisionReview --> Blocked: collision
  Blocked --> ActionQueue: owner + next_action + due_date
  ActionQueue --> G2_SourceCoverage: source task
  ActionQueue --> G3_EditionCheck: edition task
  ActionQueue --> G5_CollisionReview: collision task

  ReadyForMinistryReview --> Caveat: export footer
  note right of Caveat
    DRAFT / EXPERT REVIEW
    Dependency/evidence map, not legal opinion
    No current/latest wording before approved_l3 + current_edition_verified
  end note
